Here is the translation:

Say the farmer's field was taken away, I would not settle in that place; 
My friend has been given a seat, after him it will be my turn to come and prostrate.

Fake company you are fake friend; 
If you know the truth then do you parade; 
We will consider then.

Here are the translations:

Stayed at home, no one knows my address; 
Done for myself, that's how I've spent my life.
